                                <span class="timeline-icon red"></span>
                                <span class="timeline-date">08:25 am</span>
                                <h1 class="red">USB攜出記錄</h1>
                                <p>小明透過USB帶走了 : veryimportant.docx</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="timeline-item alt">
                    <div class="timeline-desk">
                        <div class="panel">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <span class="arrow-alt"></span>
                                <span class="timeline-icon green"></span>
                                <span class="timeline-date">10:00 am</span>
                                <h1 class="green">非法上網記錄</h1>
                                <p>
                                    <a href="#">Charmmy</a> 瀏覽了非法網站 <span>
                                        <a href="#" class="green">Facebook</a>
                                    </span>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-desk">
                        <div class="panel">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <span class="arrow"></span>
                                <span class="timeline-icon blue"></span>
                                <span class="timeline-date">11:35 am</span>
                                <h1 class="blue">硬體變更</h1>
                                <p>
                                    <a href="#">系統變更記錄</a> 違規聊天記錄, 變更項目 <span>
                                        <a href="#" class="blue">記憶體</a>
                                    </span>
                                </p>
                                <div class="album">
                                    <a href="#">
                                        <img alt="" src="/Static/img/sm-img-1.jpg">
                                    </a>
                                    <a href="#">
                                        <img alt="" src="/Static/img/sm-img-2.jpg">
                                    </a>
                                    <a href="#">
                                        <img alt="" src="/Static/img/sm-img-3.jpg">
                                    </a>
                                    <a href="#">
                                        <img alt="" src="/Static/img/sm-img-1.jpg">
                                    </a>
                                    <a href="#">
                                        <img alt="" src="/Static/img/sm-img-2.jpg">
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="timeline-item alt">
                    <div class="timeline-desk">
                        <div class="panel">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <span class="arrow-alt"></span>
                                <span class="timeline-icon purple"></span>
                                <span class="timeline-date">3:20 pm</span>
                                <h1 class="purple">聊天記錄</h1>
                                <p>Charmmy違反企業聊天規則</p>
                                <div class="notification">
                                    <i class=" fa fa-exclamation-sign"></i> 違法關鍵字 <a href="#">抱抱</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-desk">
                        <div class="panel">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <span class="arrow"></span>
                                <span class="timeline-icon light-green"></span>
                                <span class="timeline-date">07:49 pm</span>
                                <h1 class="light-green">非法軟體執行</h1>
                                <p>
                                    <a href="#">Dora</a> 執行了非法軟體: <span>
